des: Deccan Chronicle brings you the latest news, views, analysis and images from India and the world.Deccan Chronicle is an Indian English-language daily newspaper. It is published in Hyderabad, Telangana by Deccan Chronicle Holdings Limited. The newspaper's name derives from the originating place, the Deccan regions of India.
